query:
INSERT INTO building_codes (code, title, edition, jurisdiction, year, effectiveDate, status, isLatest, isActive, lastVerified)
VALUES 
  ('nbc-2025', 'National Building Code of Canada 2025', '2025', 'Canada', 2025, 'Proposed', 'proposed', 1, 1, NOW()),
  ('nbc-2020', 'National Building Code of Canada 2020', '2020', 'Canada', 2020, '2020', 'active', 0, 1, NOW()),
  ('obc-2024', 'Ontario Building Code 2024', '2024', 'Ontario', 2024, 'January 1, 2025', 'active', 1, 1, NOW()),
  ('bcbc-2024', 'British Columbia Building Code 2024', '2024', 'British Columbia', 2024, 'March 8, 2024', 'active', 1, 1, NOW()),
  ('abc-2023', 'Alberta Building Code 2023', '2023', 'Alberta', 2023, 'May 1, 2024', 'active', 1, 1, NOW()),
  ('ibc-2024', 'International Building Code 2024', '2024', 'International', 2024, '2024', 'active', 1, 1, NOW())
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE
  title = VALUES(title),
  edition = VALUES(edition),
  jurisdiction = VALUES(jurisdiction),
  year = VALUES(year),
  effectiveDate = VALUES(effectiveDate),
  status = VALUES(status),
  isLatest = VALUES(isLatest),
  lastVerified = NOW();
